<note n="0919011" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0919011">（佛說）＋廣【宋】【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0919012" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0919012">〔一卷〕－【宋】【元】【明】<choice cb:resp="#resp3"><corr>＊</corr><sic><space quantity="0"/></sic></choice></note>
<note n="0919014" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0919014">天竺三藏＝三藏法師【宋】【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0920001" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0920001">察＋（一不淨想者）五字【宋】【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0920002" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0920002">大＝太【宋】【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0920004" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0920004">聞＝問【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note>
<note n="0920005" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0920005">得＋（非）【宋】【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0920007" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0920007">土＝士【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note>
<note n="0921001" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0921001">然＝律【宋】【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0921002" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0921002">相＝想【宋】【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0921004" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0921004">〔今〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0921005" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0921005">〔不〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0921006" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0921006">恒喜＝恒戲【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note>
<note n="0922001" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0922001">二心猗＝三心猗【宋】【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0922002" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0922002">永＋（斷）【宋】【元】【明】</note>
</p>
